    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/cbd556f1b68748575a9ba17967d15c54.poster.avif?t=1654067803\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/cbd556f1b68748575a9ba17967d15c54.webm?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/cbd556f1b68748575a9ba17967d15c54.mp4?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Severed Steel》是一款单人FPS游戏，具有流畅的特技系统、可摧毁的立体像素环境、大量的子弹时间，以及独特的独臂主人公。主人公就是你，你扣动扳机，穿上钢头靴，来对抗上层组织的坏人。飞檐走壁、俯冲、翻转和滑行，通过这一连串的动作击倒每一个敌人。<br><br><strong>主要特点</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独一无二的战士</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/341021d5d50c66575b42745758594a4a.poster.avif?t=1654067803\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/341021d5d50c66575b42745758594a4a.webm?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/341021d5d50c66575b42745758594a4a.mp4?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扮演灵活的独臂神枪手斯蒂尔来执行任务。枪支不能重新填充子弹，所以要做到弹无虚发，并准备好从敌人冰冷的手中夺取已上膛的武器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >风格特异的战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/f7e6c643d8a2961aa0101a1e62f7ea13.poster.avif?t=1654067803\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/f7e6c643d8a2961aa0101a1e62f7ea13.webm?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/f7e6c643d8a2961aa0101a1e62f7ea13.mp4?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>躲闪子弹、跳墙、滑踢、投掷武器——不惜一切代价，在激烈疯狂的枪战中独领风骚。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完全可摧毁的环境</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/196c496fe35bcaa18947aa8dfe0011d4.poster.avif?t=1654067803\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/196c496fe35bcaa18947aa8dfe0011d4.webm?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/196c496fe35bcaa18947aa8dfe0011d4.mp4?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>用锋利的4.7毫米子弹打穿石膏，用0.50口径的弹头打穿厚重的混凝土墙，或者用手臂加农炮打穿任何铜墙铁壁。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态人工智能</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/24871e338937c673506ffb965137d70b.poster.avif?t=1654067803\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/24871e338937c673506ffb965137d70b.webm?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/24871e338937c673506ffb965137d70b.mp4?t=1654067803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>采用动态、无脚本、团战的人工智能，没有一模一样的战斗。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >辅助功能</h2>一系列可调整的功能设置，例如难度、视效、音频、控制、导航等更多<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关卡编辑器（含Steam创意工坊支持）</h2>创建关卡并与社区分享。注意：此功能仍在测试中，将在推出后继续更新<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1631910/extras/241d9c4f581bf6b6cf18297fc06cbe7c.avif?t=1654067803\" width=610 height=154 /></span>",
